    <h3> Student Application Status Form </h3>

    Upon completion of your form you will have been provided with a unique code to use to check the status of your
    approval request.<br>
    Visit <a href="/public/ApplicationStatusForm">The Application Status Form</a> and in the fields provided, enter your
    student number, and company's name.<br>
    Where prompted, enter your given code and click on the button at the bottom of the screen to submit the form and see
    your application status.<br>
